## Authorization

### Role-Based Access Control

```typescript
function hasPermission(role: Role, required: string): boolean {
  return role === 'admin' || permissions[role].includes(required)
}
```

### Resource Ownership

```typescript
const doc = await db.document.findUnique({ where: { id } })
if (doc.ownerId !== userId) throw new Error('Unauthorized access')
```

