## ARIA Security

```typescript
// ✅ Accurate
<button aria-label="Close dialog" onClick={() => setIsOpen(false)}>✕</button>

// ❌ Misleading (security risk for screen readers)
<button aria-label="View profile" onClick={handleDelete}>✕</button>
```

Trap focus in modals. Tab cycles through focusable elements, Escape closes.

---

## PR Security Checklist

- [ ] Inputs validated with Zod, server-side
- [ ] No hardcoded secrets (use process.env)
- [ ] CSP + HSTS + X-Frame-Options headers set
- [ ] Sensitive data not in client bundles
- [ ] Errors don't leak stack traces

